<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7360> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7360" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Tr. pl. and Leg., lieut. See MRR 2.469, 483. Wiseman, taking Cicero's list in Leg. Man. 58 as presented in the order of seniority, attributes his tribunate and his legateship in successive years to the period before 81 (CQ 14, 1964, 122-123) but in NM 230, no. 170, adds (or tr. pl. 68, leg. 67?); see also Syme JRS 53, 1963, 55-60-RP 2.557-565; Historia 13, 1964, 106-RP 2.583.\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6776> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6776" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/3> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Cic. Leg. Man. 58. See above, Tribunes of the Plebs of uncertain date. Before 66." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6629> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6629" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/3> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "One of a group named by Cicero as examples of persons who held the tribunate in one year and were Legates the next (Cic. Leg. Man. 58, 66 B. C.)." .
